data.title: Central Pennsylvania Music Hall of Fame
data.meta_description: A non-profit organization designed to recognize, support, and grow the overall music scene in central Pennsylvania.  The Central Pennsylvania Music Hall of Fame strives to enhance the legacy of those who write, perform, record, produce, support, host, and educate in our area.  Not only will there be members elected to the Central Pennsylvania Music Hall of Fame, but there will also be an annual red-carpet awards show!  Think the Grammy's--on a local level!
data.meta_site_name: Central Pennsylvania Music Hall of Fame
data.text:
Explore our multi-room museum of autographed albums, guitars, relics, and more from Central PA's finest music artists! Come take a FREE self-guided tour (7am-3pm)!

The CPMHOF shares its space with the Englewood Roasting Company; so grab a coffee/lunch, and embrace our area's vast music history!
